Package com.cafean.client.ui.swing.accordion

Class DefaultAccordionModel<Type>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.client.ui.swing.accordion.AbstractAccordionModel
      • com.cafean.client.ui.swing.accordion.DefaultAccordionModel<Type>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AccordionModel
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NavigatorAccordionModel
    public class DefaultAccordionModel<Type>
extends AbstractAccordionModel
    The default implementation of the AccordionModel interface. It functions similarly to a Vector (and in fact, represents its data internally with a Vector object), and has methods that directly match most Vector methods.
